Title: Torsionless T-selfdual Affine NA Toda Models
Authors: J.F. Gomes, E. P. Gueuvoghlanian, G.M. Sotkov and A.H. Zimerman
Comments: typos corrected, talk given at the VI International Wigner Symposium,
  Istambul, Turkey, 16-22 August,1999
\\
  A general construction of affine Non Abelian Toda models in terms of gauged
two loop WZNW model is discussed. In particular we find the
 Lie algebraic condition defining a subclass of {\it T-selfdual torsionless NA
Toda models} and their zero curvature representation.
